* All-women shortlists
* Diversity (business)
* Equality of opportunity vs Equality of outcome
* Gender quota
* Numerus clausus
* Racism, Anti-racism
* Reverse discrimination, Discrimination
*&quot;Regents of the University of California v. Bakke&quot;

